# Production (`npm run build`): set your deployed API (no trailing slash).
# VITE_API_URL=https://your-api.example.com
#
# Local dev: leave VITE_API_URL unset so the app calls /api and Vite proxies to http://127.0.0.1:8000.
# That avoids CORS when you open the UI at 127.0.0.1 or a phone/LAN URL instead of localhost.
